{"tid":846570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇男既每個月都會有幾日特別頹","createTime":"2018-10-03T13:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T15:54:55.000Z","uid":57308,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbabb6d7940da0a788aa212de3d7242a46d6377","tid":846570,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都好頹廢，今晚ot完更加難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9776fcd6fc95f5f7a48655abe9d2c797b8a109","tid":846570,"uid":103759,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來M果幾日"},{"pid":"32591198bcd6726da67fd5b4bd6c13c57041114b","tid":846570,"uid":57308,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"女性的生理期是每一個月一次，是由於子宮內膜脫落而引起子宮出血的症狀。而醫學專家認為，男人也有生理期，且周期跟女性差不多，為28天。在這個周期內，男性會像女性一樣，會出現心情低落、情緒失控、免疫力低下等現象。<br />\n<br />\n　　男性由於體內激素和神經遞質的影響，生理系統也同樣擁有自己的周期變化。只不過男性生理期的表現並不像女性那麼明顯，也不如女性月經來得那麼定時，而且不少人常常把它歸咎於天氣、飲食的影響或工作的壓力，所以往往難以察覺。而在男性生理期時，男人體內睾丸酮、雄激素的含量呈下降趨勢，處於最低點。"},{"pid":"5259b23684dcd43a2a9a47045b9266aa91655954","tid":846570,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff9776fcd6fc95f5f7a48655abe9d2c797b8a109","tid":846570,"uid":103759,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n來M果幾日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"好想轉工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif